// Purpose: // Utility function used to fragment external container storage into multiple subfolders based on record creation date // History: // 10/2/19 Mislav: Created custom function. // Notes: // Use this custom function in Field options > Storage > Container > Open storage // Do NOT use Self for the table and/or field name CF parameters. The external storage calculation doesn't seem to reference Self correctly. Let ( _date = If ( IsEmpty ( creationDate ) ; "0000-00" ; Let ( _date = GetAsDate ( creationDate ) ; Year ( _date ) & "-" & Right ( 0 & Month ( _date ) ; 2 ) ) ) ; tableName & "/" & fieldName & "/" & _date & "/" )

// Signature: // GetFileMakerVersionMajor // Purpose: // Detects major component of current FileMaker application version // Parameters: // None // Result: // Returns major component of current FileMaker application version // For example, if FileMaker application version is 19.2.1, this custom function will return 19 // Dependencies: // None // History: // Created: Mislav Kos <mkos@soliantconsulting.com> GetAsNumber ( GetValue ( Substitute ( RightWords ( Get ( applicationVersion ) ; 1 ) ; "." ; ¶ ) ; 1 ) )

// Signature: // GetFileMakerVersionMinor // Purpose: // Detects minor component of current FileMaker application version // Parameters: // None // Result: // Returns minor component of current FileMaker application version // For example, if FileMaker application version is 19.2.1, this custom function will return 2 // Dependencies: // None // History: // Created: Mislav Kos <mkos@soliantconsulting.com> GetAsNumber ( GetValue ( Substitute ( RightWords ( Get ( applicationVersion ) ; 1 ) ; "." ; ¶ ) ; 2 ) )

// Signature: // GetFileMakerVersionPatch // Purpose: // Detects patch component of current FileMaker application version // Parameters: // None // Result: // Returns patch component of current FileMaker application version // For example, if FileMaker application version is 19.2.1, this custom function will return 1 // Dependencies: // None // History: // Created: Mislav Kos <mkos@soliantconsulting.com> GetAsNumber ( GetValue ( Substitute ( RightWords ( Get ( applicationVersion ) ; 1 ) ; "." ; ¶ ) ; 3 ) )
